### Naming Preview

Based on your account strategy and naming conventions:

{%- if account_strategy == 'Single Account' %}
**Strategy:** Single Account — All components in database name

**Example Database Name:** `{{ data_product_domain | upper }}_{{ data_product_name | upper }}_RAW_{{ data_product_environment | upper }}`

{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Environment-based)' %}
**Strategy:** Environment-based — Environment is at account level (not in database name)

**Example Database Name:** `{{ data_product_domain | upper }}_{{ data_product_name | upper }}_RAW`

{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Domain-based)' %}
**Strategy:** Domain-based — Domain is at account level (not in database name)

**Example Database Name:** `{{ data_product_name | upper }}_RAW_{{ data_product_environment | upper }}`

{%- elif account_strategy == 'Multi-Account (Domain + Environment)' %}
**Strategy:** Domain + Environment — Both are at account level (not in database name)

**Example Database Name:** `{{ data_product_name | upper }}_RAW`

{%- endif %}

